+Variables:
+- `sym`: symbol filter
+- `bucket`: exec_regime_bucket filter
+
+Panels:
+- microprice divergence vs mid + microprice shift
+- DW OBI (raw + robust-z)
+- DW OBI stability score + stable flag
+- queue imbalance aggregates (L1..L5)
+- depth shape: slope imbalance (normalized) + convexity imbalance
+
+Runbook: `/runbooks/world_practice_lob_pressure_v1.md`
